## Features
**jdbc**

- support JDBC4 CLOB and BLOB in PreparedStatement parameters ([9515a80](https://github.com/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/commits/9515a80))

**sqlite**

- upgrade to sqlite 3.50.3 ([ef4e649](https://github.com/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/commits/ef4e649))

**unscoped**

- build android native lib with 16kb page size ([8548d1c](https://github.com/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/commits/8548d1c)), closes [#1296](https://github.com/xerial/sqlite-jdbc/issues/1296)

