<user_query>
Root Layout:

 AnchorPane (main container)

Inside AnchorPane:

 Label – "Add Product to Cart" (screen title)

 TextField – Quantity input (user enters how many units to add)

 ComboBox – Select product variant (e.g., size, flavor, weight)

 HBox – Contains two RadioButtons (e.g., "Home Delivery" / "Pickup") for delivery method selection

 DatePicker – Choose delivery or pickup date

 Button – "Add to Cart" (main action)

 TableView – Mini cart preview showing:

 TableColumn: Product Name

 TableColumn: Quantity

